description: This file contains Dart classes that implement repositories for managing various data entities such as workouts, diets, clients, and protocols. Each repository provides methods for CRUD operations interacting with an API via an ApiClient.

classes.name: WorkoutsRepository
classes.description: Repository for workout plans, providing methods to list, create, retrieve by ID, update, and delete workouts.

classes.name: DietRepository
classes.description: Repository for diet plans, providing standard CRUD operations.

classes.name: ClientsRepository
classes.description: Repository for client data management with CRUD operations.

classes.name: ProtocolsRepository
classes.description: Repository for protocol goals with methods for listing, creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting protocol data.

methods.name: list
methods.description: Fetches a paginated list of entities from the server.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new entity using provided payload.

methods.name: getById
methods.description: Retrieves a specific entity by its ID.

methods.name: update
methods.description: Updates an existing entity with new data.

methods.name: delete
methods.description: Deletes an entity by its ID.
